-- Merkel May Boycott Football Event in Ukraine, Spiegel Reports
-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 2012-04-29T14:35:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-29/merkel-may-boycott-football-event-in-ukraine-spiegel-reports.html
German Chancellor Angela Merkel may
boycott the European soccer championship in Ukraine in June amid
reports of mistreatment and abuse against jailed opposition
leader  Yulia Tymoshenko , Der Spiegel reported, without saying
where it got the information.  If Tymoshenko is not released by the time the tournament
starts, Merkel wants to recommend to her ministers not to
attend, Der Spiegel said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Julie Cruz in Frankfurt at 
 jcruz6@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Sara Marley at   smarley1@bloomberg.net  